WEBVTT

00:05:25.875 --> 00:05:30.101
his home, his land,
his neighbors hating him.

00:05:30.125 --> 00:05:33.309
And I could risk
getting my organization sued,

00:05:33.333 --> 00:05:35.851
or being the reason
that he would lose everything,

00:05:35.875 --> 00:05:39.125
but we had to do it anyway.

00:05:41.583 --> 00:05:44.143
"The New York Times" broke the story

00:05:44.167 --> 00:05:46.518
and within 24 hours,

00:05:46.542 --> 00:05:50.184
a million people had seen our video.

00:05:50.208 --> 00:05:52.893
It went viral by every definition,

00:05:52.917 --> 00:05:56.059
and suddenly we had this global platform

00:05:56.083 --> 00:05:59.125
for talking about factory farming.